data.description: Single story, 4 bed, 2 bath home with open floor plan. Enjoy little to no electric bills due to solar panels on home. Owner will supply monitored alarm system and yard maintenance. Refrigerator, washer, and dryer included. This home features wood laminate flooring and granite. There is a large master suite with upgraded master bath and spacious walk-in closet. Renters insurance required. Available for move in December 20th.
